{"tid":1245411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有少少覺得今日似6月15號","createTime":"2019-06-20T09:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T10:57:43.000Z","uid":1834,"like":23,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"76b4ee4f2893627d5aef7171bd49ccc2090ef055","tid":1245411,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:39:45.000Z","msg":"突然又一堆人呼籲叫人唔好衝<br />\n同6月15號一樣<br />\n又係一班人出黎叫人冷靜<br />\n6月16直頭成個金鐘都無嘜差人,因為已經知道香港人暴力潔癖唔會沖<br />\n成班差佬放曬假,你同我講無打龍通我都唔撚信<br />\n<br />\n班垃圾用完個人數打飛機就散水<br />\n咩不撤不退,到第二朝夏愨得返200個人<br />\n4大訴求一樣都做唔到<br />\n其實佢地覺唔覺得16號好撚失敗?<br />\n<br />\n明明講到明兄弟爬山各有各做<br />\n16號晚係度捉鬼,水馬拎黎防禦o既,差佬突擊都有得隔一隔<br />\n成日話人衝,衝條撚咩,根本個個都知道太少人無得衝/守<br />\n咁都可以當人係鬼,同雨革有咩分別?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1.反省雨傘失敗,拒督灰﹑割蓆﹑拖延﹑捉鬼</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n到宜家見D人話聽日要行動升級D左膠又出返曬黎<br />\n話咩無民意受權,飯民唔支持<br />\n強行將200萬人遊行o既民意分割話佢地唔想勇武派衝<br />\n勇武派12號唔衝o既話條條例2/3讀左啦柒頭<br />\n不論普通市民定係勇武派佢地o既目標其實一致<br />\n講咩民意授唔授權,講到勇武派唔係市民咁<br />\n同政府早年d新聞稿一樣(網民呢樣網民o個樣)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2.千其唔好被輿論分化,200萬入邊都包含勇武派</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港特有o既示弱式示威一早畀政府定義做暴動/顏色革命<br />\n班人都仲話要扮慘,逼我做中國人仲唔撚夠慘咩?仲要扮慘?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3.香港人已經夠慘,輿論已經傾向市民,香港人應該盡地一舖</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n班左膠最叻就係問人<br />\n「衝邊?衝黎做咩?」<br />\n「有冇諗過行出嚟嘅市民，只係想和平理性向政府表達訴求？」<br />\n「有冇諗過你只諗自己，冇為整體社會著想？」<br />\n行得上前線已經冒好大風險,仲要畀你班人話自私<br />\n如果尻行有用香港根本唔會有勇武派<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4.大家應該要知道和平o既市民行出黎和平表達完意見<br />\n如果無勇武派同你向政府施壓根本唔會有用</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後一點,唔好諗住G20一定幫到你<br />\n美國佬幫香港固然好,但係唔係應份,<br />\n當年英國佬將香港雙手奉上<br />\n畀你拖到G20,美國佬又隻字不提<br />\n到時已經民怨消耗得七七八八,你想再施壓已經好難<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5.香港人o既命運係香港人手中,唔好咁肯定人地會幫你,自己o既未來自己去爭取</span></strong>"},{"pid":"008dc87ff03d501cb81f9bd2a6aaf42c98e90a85","tid":1245411,"uid":41389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘<br />\n唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘<br />\n唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘<br />\n唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘<br />\n唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n4個地點步程10分鐘內：禮賓 政總 警總等 <br />\n<br />\n人未齊未衝得做咩好？ 唔好阻人返工！！！<br />\n香港人平時唔係好想打風有假放既咩？ 而家比個藉口大家聽日無工返就屌曬聲？<br />\n利申發夢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其他野可以遲d做無所謂 <strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">G20呢d大好機會錯失左就一世</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d99eca05c22e73f82d5b7d4a46c74ed8db5f6db6","tid":1245411,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:40:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a><br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f8adb10fc7794b88fd1c707f39a6b1f641cdfde6","tid":1245411,"uid":156936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"【請為621廣泛報料，聽朝七點，政總集合】<br />\n【不內哄、不分化、各自上山】<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>======20/6/2019 17:00更新======</strong></span><br />\n立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府警察勢力分報圖，持續收料，一直更新。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rtOBOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rtOBOy.jpg&h=eae4919c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歡迎加入討論: <strong>圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1</a><br />\n<strong>更多細節請用追故模式</strong><br />\n===============================<br />\n禮賓府高空、地則及2018香港地圖懶人包<br />\n===============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34yGdCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34yGdCf.jpg&h=2aced7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gB8C11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gB8C11.jpg&h=f5e08abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aA1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aA1c0.jpg&h=0cd9b552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禮賓府交通路線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n====================<br />\n禮賓府建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n1.急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n2.立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港親共商店地圖</span></span></strong><br />\n消費前，睇下呢個地圖！斷親共收入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IKNf97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IKNf97&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D5IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=8e9e83e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IKNf97</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府全部都相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7858e85d0165ca45212c95badb66629c3ec8e1da","tid":1245411,"uid":174752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"成日話咩最後一戰，人地行動就話民心民意最緊要，你最後一戰輸左民心民意有撚用咩，維穩就維穩la<br />\n<br />\n根本依家係612之後再冇爭取後任何野，大家真係對唔對得住犧牲左既人"},{"pid":"8a18b6c119aea205fbb430f8a4fdb1bc47a605a3","tid":1245411,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7858e85d0165ca45212c95badb66629c3ec8e1da","tid":1245411,"uid":174752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"成日話咩最後一戰，人地行動就話民心民意最緊要，你最後一戰輸左民心民意有撚用咩，維穩就維穩la<br />\n<br />\n根本依家係612之後再冇爭取後任何野，大家真係對唔對得住犧牲左既人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"香港人好多都好現實,結果論<br />\n成功就有民意支持"},{"pid":"8d1750e19c9b83432d191088c4519ea5d2783048","tid":1245411,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a18b6c119aea205fbb430f8a4fdb1bc47a605a3","tid":1245411,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7858e85d0165ca45212c95badb66629c3ec8e1da","tid":1245411,"uid":174752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"成日話咩最後一戰，人地行動就話民心民意最緊要，你最後一戰輸左民心民意有撚用咩，維穩就維穩la<br />\n<br />\n根本依家係612之後再冇爭取後任何野，大家真係對唔對得住犧牲左既人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"香港人好多都好現實,結果論<br />\n成功就有民意支持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"咁事前就唔應該用民意做擋箭牌，偽名題，用黎拖延時間"},{"pid":"9cbd872078775c892ece52476a885165011e2fef","tid":1245411,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d